<h4 class="ez_pagetitle">Stats Dashboard and Downloadable PDF's</h4>
<div id="ez_msg">
<div id="ez_header">
<span class="ez_label">From:</span> David Kobia &lt;david@...&gt;<br />
<span class="ez_label">Date:</span> Thu, 11 Feb 2010 10:23:00 -0500<br />
</div>
<pre>Patrick brought up a very interesting point about a &quot;Create Situation
Report&quot; button within an Ushahidi deployment that would create a
downloadable PDF from the main page. I just wanted to push this
discussion into the mailing list so that we can hopefully get this
feature built in. Attached is a sample report from Kenya, along with a
mock of a simplified version of what the pdf might look like.

Since we're on the subject of stats, you guys should also look at the
Feltron Reports that have inspired many -
<a href="http://feltron.com/index.php?/content/2008_annual_report/P1/">http://feltron.com/index.php?/content/2008_annual_report/P1/</a>

Other Links:
- <a href="http://www.fpdf.org/">http://www.fpdf.org/</a>
- <a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/html2fpdf/">http://sourceforge.net/projects/html2fpdf/</a>
</pre><br /><h4>Attachments:</h4>
